_sText:
This is my first map that I have made in hammer, and my first map for CS:S
The map is quite small so there will be a lot of action every round.
There are two main snipe points, one at each end of the map (accessible by ladder) and near the CT spawn there are several obstacles to hide behind for cover. At the T side, there are catwalks and a room where you can reach a snipe point which covers the central area of the map.
